📚 Quiz App - Programming Practice
A cross-language coding quiz app designed to help learners practice and test their knowledge in any programming language. The app features three difficulty levels — Beginner, Intermediate, and Advanced — with a variety of multiple-choice coding-related questions.

🧠 Features
🔤 Supports multiple languages (C, C++, Python, Java, JavaScript, etc.)

🧩 3 Levels of Difficulty:

Beginner – Basic syntax and concepts

Intermediate – Loops, conditions, arrays, functions

Advanced – Data Structures, OOP, Algorithms

✅ Real-time scoring and feedback

🗃️ Question bank stored in JSON or database

